author: Soo Kim
title: Dr. Phil Defends Opening Up America, Compares Coronavirus Death Rate to Car and Swimming Pool Accidents
description: The television personality warned the impact of the current lockdown orders in the U.S. may see "more deaths across time than the actual virus will itself."
content:
The novel coronavirus outbreak in the U.S. has seen much of the country remain in lockdown, with several states issuing "stay-at-home" orders in a bid to help curb the spread of the virus.
